[
    {
        "start": 0.0,
        "end": 12.06,
        "text": "Ted Talks are recorded live at the Ted Conference and partner events.",
        "score": 0.0,
        "label": "Neutral"
    },
    {
        "start": 12.06,
        "end": 15.280000000000001,
        "text": "This episode features musician Andrew Bird.",
        "score": 0.0,
        "label": "Neutral"
    },
    {
        "start": 15.280000000000001,
        "end": 18.28,
        "text": "Here's Andrew Bird.",
        "score": 0.0,
        "label": "Neutral"
    },
    {
        "start": 18.28,
        "end": 25.28,
        "text": "Well, there's lots to talk about, and I think I'm just going to play to start on.",
        "score": 0.5423,
        "label": "Positive"
    },
    {
        "start": 228.78,
        "end": 235.28,
        "text": "So, feed the fishes.",
        "score": 0.0,
        "label": "Neutral"
    },
    {
        "start": 236.46,
        "end": 243.46,
        "text": "Sing me happy birthday.",
        "score": 0.5719,
        "label": "Positive"
    },
    {
        "start": 243.46,
        "end": 250.46,
        "text": "The luck it's going to be.",
        "score": 0.4588,
        "label": "Positive"
    },
    {
        "start": 250.46,
        "end": 256.46,
        "text": "Here are the...",
        "score": 0.0,
        "label": "Neutral"
    },
    {
        "start": 318.28,
        "end": 325.9,
        "text": "Wow.",
        "score": 0.5859,
        "label": "Positive"
    },
    {
        "start": 348.28,
        "end": 354.76,
        "text": "Alright, so I wanted to do something special today. I want to debut a new song that I've",
        "score": 0.6124,
        "label": "Positive"
    },
    {
        "start": 354.76,
        "end": 360.52,
        "text": "been working on in the last five or six months. And there's a few things more thrilling",
        "score": 0.5256,
        "label": "Positive"
    },
    {
        "start": 360.52,
        "end": 365.64,
        "text": "than playing a song for the first time in front of an audience, especially when it's",
        "score": 0.2023,
        "label": "Positive"
    },
    {
        "start": 365.64,
        "end": 373.4,
        "text": "half finished. So I'm kind of hoping some conversations here might help me finish it,",
        "score": 0.6378,
        "label": "Positive"
    },
    {
        "start": 373.4,
        "end": 379.47999999999996,
        "text": "because it gets into all sorts of crazy realms. And so this is basically a song about",
        "score": -0.34,
        "label": "Negative"
    },
    {
        "start": 380.52,
        "end": 385.64,
        "text": "loops, but not the kind of loops that I make up here. They're feedback loops. And in the audio",
        "score": 0.0,
        "label": "Neutral"
    },
    {
        "start": 385.64,
        "end": 393.64,
        "text": "world, that's kind of, that's when the microphone gets too close to its sound source, and then it gets",
        "score": 0.0,
        "label": "Neutral"
    },
    {
        "start": 393.64,
        "end": 398.76,
        "text": "in this self-destructive loop that creates a very unpleasant sound. I'm going to demonstrate for you.",
        "score": -0.3167,
        "label": "Negative"
    },
    {
        "start": 398.76,
        "end": 404.84,
        "text": "I'm not going to hurt you, though.",
        "score": 0.4168,
        "label": "Positive"
    },
    {
        "start": 404.84,
        "end": 415.8,
        "text": "This is a loop, feedback loop. This is a loop, feedback loop. This is a loop, feedback loop.",
        "score": 0.0,
        "label": "Neutral"
    },
    {
        "start": 429.56,
        "end": 437.8,
        "text": "Alright, I don't know if that was necessary. But my point is it's the sound of self-destruction.",
        "score": 0.128,
        "label": "Positive"
    },
    {
        "start": 441.71999999999997,
        "end": 447.8,
        "text": "And I've been thinking about how that applies across a whole spectrum of realms from the,",
        "score": 0.0,
        "label": "Neutral"
    },
    {
        "start": 447.8,
        "end": 454.28,
        "text": "say, the ecological, okay? There seems to be a rule in nature that if you get too close to where",
        "score": 0.2263,
        "label": "Positive"
    },
    {
        "start": 455.0,
        "end": 461.4,
        "text": "you came from, it gets ugly. So like you can't feed cows their own brains and you get mad,",
        "score": -0.5729,
        "label": "Negative"
    },
    {
        "start": 461.4,
        "end": 467.79999999999995,
        "text": "or you get mad cow disease and inbreeding and incest. And let's see, what's the other one?",
        "score": -0.4939,
        "label": "Negative"
    },
    {
        "start": 468.76,
        "end": 473.79999999999995,
        "text": "Biological, there's autoimmune diseases where the body attacks itself, little two,",
        "score": -0.4404,
        "label": "Negative"
    },
    {
        "start": 474.35999999999996,
        "end": 480.91999999999996,
        "text": "overzealously, and destroys the host, the person. And then,",
        "score": -0.5574,
        "label": "Negative"
    },
    {
        "start": 481.56,
        "end": 487.16,
        "text": "okay, this is where we get to the song, kind of bridges the gap to the emotional,",
        "score": 0.3612,
        "label": "Positive"
    },
    {
        "start": 488.04,
        "end": 494.76,
        "text": "because although I've used scientific terms and in songs, it's very difficult sometimes to make",
        "score": -0.4201,
        "label": "Negative"
    },
    {
        "start": 494.76,
        "end": 500.12,
        "text": "them lyrical. And there's some things you just don't need to have in songs. But",
        "score": 0.0,
        "label": "Neutral"
    },
    {
        "start": 502.20000000000005,
        "end": 509.40000000000003,
        "text": "so I'm trying to bridge this gap between this idea and this melody. And so I don't know if you've",
        "score": 0.0,
        "label": "Neutral"
    },
    {
        "start": 509.4,
        "end": 516.84,
        "text": "ever had this, but when I close my eyes sometimes and try to sleep, I can't stop thinking about my",
        "score": 0.3252,
        "label": "Positive"
    },
    {
        "start": 516.84,
        "end": 524.12,
        "text": "own eyes. And it's like your eyes start straining to see themselves. That's what it feels like to me.",
        "score": 0.4019,
        "label": "Positive"
    },
    {
        "start": 524.12,
        "end": 530.84,
        "text": "It's not pleasant. I'm sorry if I put that idea in your head. But it's impossible, of course,",
        "score": -0.1877,
        "label": "Negative"
    },
    {
        "start": 530.84,
        "end": 535.72,
        "text": "for your eyes to see themselves, but they seem to be trying. And so that's getting a little more",
        "score": 0.0,
        "label": "Neutral"
    },
    {
        "start": 535.72,
        "end": 541.4,
        "text": "closer to like a personal experience. And then, or ears being able to hear themselves. It's",
        "score": 0.3612,
        "label": "Positive"
    },
    {
        "start": 541.4,
        "end": 548.9200000000001,
        "text": "just it's impossible. That is that's the thing. So I've been working on this song that mentions",
        "score": 0.0,
        "label": "Neutral"
    },
    {
        "start": 548.9200000000001,
        "end": 556.52,
        "text": "these things. And then also imagines a person who's been so successful at defending themselves",
        "score": 0.7065,
        "label": "Positive"
    },
    {
        "start": 556.52,
        "end": 563.72,
        "text": "from heartbreak that they're left to do the deed themselves. If that's possible and that's what",
        "score": -0.5719,
        "label": "Negative"
    },
    {
        "start": 563.72,
        "end": 565.72,
        "text": "the someone is asking.",
        "score": 0.0,
        "label": "Neutral"
    },
